column5: well was up in the kawarthas  11-18 and managed to get a new PB large mouth :thumbsup_anim:  missed my chance at a musky out of the kayak tho it came up right beside me was awsome
nice bucket.  it's amazing how  big their yaps are.
Holy crap. You could stick your whole head in there
nice feeesh mang  did it take you for a ride on the yak ?
That is a big mouth indeed. Looks a bit too big for the rest of the fish.  Nice fish none the less and congrats on the PB!
Woo Hoo!  Congrads on that BIG BASS! Did you get a weight on her or can I play the guessing game? I'm gonna say 5.10lbs  Thanks for sharing, MTBF
Great catch. Also curious of the weight? What did you catch that PIG on?  Dirk
nice man, huuge mouth on that, be fun to grab.
nice bucket there im wondering to how heavy was it looks like it was over 5lbs maybe more maybe less
i got no idea what she weighed was 21' long and got her on a big o, amazing watching them jump
